text:
Yuika was right.
The local talk was a big hit.

Having fun and enjoying delicious food,
which also reflects in our work!

Well, it's just a basic principle...
...Why does Yuika pull away when praised...!?

Because!
Praise and appeal are jokes!

P-tan comes at you with sincere kindness!
They're different kinds of people~!

What's wrong with being moved by the
good qualities of the one in charge?

That's why I'm saying even that...
...is too straightforward.
